# Particle Effects

## Objective
Enhance the existing GSAP animations with particle bursts for major achievements.

## Tasks
1. Implement a lightweight particle generation system using Canvas or DOM elements controlled by GSAP.
2. Trigger the particle burst specifically on "Level Up" events.
3. Verify performance across modern browsers to avoid stutter.
